.SH "NAME"
expiry \- check and enforce password expiration policy
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP 7
\fBexpiry\fR [\-c] [\-f]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
\fBexpiry\fR
checks (\fB\-c\fR) the current password expiration and forces (\fB\-f\fR) changes when required. It is callable as a normal user command.
